{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ae442101ec","title":"杨成武给刘志坚关于《毛主席语录》的信","origin":"唐炎明、唐亚明著：《“毛主席语录”的诞生及其他：唐平铸文革实录》，香港中文大学出版社，2019年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0d6e76739c","index":0,"year":1965,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"ae442101ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5d13a4eb3c","name":"刘志坚","type":"人物"},{"id":"e1397e909a","name":"杨成武","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"53bbb63fc8","name":"杨成武"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d1cddbf778","type":"title","text":"杨成武给刘志坚关于《毛主席语录》的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"a63715a021","type":"authors","text":"杨成武","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"10acbc46ff","type":"appellation","text":"刘副主任：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"b4e792a9c3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席指示陈伯达同志编写一本全国通用的《毛主席语录》。准备编写6万字左右，现只编写出一部分，约3万多字，给我送来一份。陈伯达同志说，这本语录是在总政和各地所编写的主席语录基础上编写的，要征求总政的意见，将来他们讨论时还要请总政派人参加。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"8cd9bda1af","type":"paragraph","text":"此事我已向林副主席报告过，林副主席指示：这是件大好事，要大力支持，需要我们做什么，我们就做什么。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"98708aab86","type":"paragraph","text":"现将我的一份稿转上，请你即告有关同志先研究，待陈伯达同志征求意见时，即可告伯达同志或参加研究。并请将结果告我一下。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"5a55e6e168","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"dbe1689661","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"},{"id":"b6dbc06ff0","type":"paragraph","text":" 杨成武1965年12月28日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec"}],"page":{"id":"497a4598af","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ae442101ec","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}